reviewText: First and Second seasons are great, but this show lasted 6 seasons!! There's no reason not to have them all out by now. Hello Cartoon Network??
they're an amazing combo set! they don't skip and they come with some fascinating special features :D
I have the first two seasons of Ed Edd n Eddy on my iPod Touch, and I am still enjoying it like I did over 10 years ago when the show first aired!
It was a gift for my daughter and she loved it.  It was exactly as shown and shipping was very prompt.  Arrived in perfect condition.
This was bought as a gift for nephews ages 12 and 18.  It is very loved and watched over and over.  I would recommend buying this.

Aside from Transformers I am an El Mongo fan of Ed Edd n Eddy. I just love this show. All the characters always make me laugh. I wish Cartoon Network would have a contest where you could be on the show (or at least being animated into a character). All my friends and I love this show and we can't get enough of em. I hope that they return for a sixth season. I also hope they make one as a refrence to Indiana Jones (like Indiana Ed or Ediana Jones etc). There is an Movie coming out where they try to find Eddy's older brother (who  is the only unseen character aside from the adults hands). So I GOT to get these die hard funny movies. ED EDD N EDDY BOOO YEAHHHHH!!!

These videos were just what my son wanted for Christmas.  He had been watching all of the episodes on the TV and was afraid they were going to stop showing the series. He was relieved to get these Season 1 and 2 videos and to see all of the episodes were included.
Santa brought this for my ten year old son and he loves it. I can't believe how funny he thinks it is. He even named our dog eddy.
So happy with the product came on time and loved this show since being a kid really wished they would release the rest of the seasons but overall this set is great lots of extras

I loved the extra stuff they put in there too! I'm definitely keeping these forever!! That way, I'll b able to point to this and say "see kids, THIS is what a quality cartoon looks like".... Sadly I doubt they will put anymore on DVD.... I bought the ones from Taiwan and they work...... But I'd love to have season 3 with a how to draw double d extra on the thing...-sighs- oh well!
i purchased this box set because if i have to watch a cartoon with my grandson aka the punk head boy it has to be something i find interesting. this would be it..
Dvds are professional and arrived on time I love the quality as well. I missed watching these as a kid it's so great to watch these and see how I still laugh at them.
there great  and interesting but there a five star only if your young so can be pretty funny and a lot of interesting stories of them worth seeing

This was my favorite childhood cartoon and having them on DVD is great. If you are a Ed, Edd 'N Eddy fan, you will enjoy this set. The only real problem was the long wait for it to arrive. But it is available for free shipping, so that makes up for the one drawback that I can find.
I am very happy with my purchase and am elated to own a dvd of these 3, let alone 2! Recommend this to anyone else who was a 90's baby and grew up watching this or any fan of the series.
so good, i remember every episode on these disks. It makes me want to go back in time when cartoons were decent.
Great quality and fun to watch, wonderful this came in a pack together instead of buying separately. We are looking for the next 2, Please come out on dvd soon!
The kids love these nuts!  I think the cartoons these days are insane.  I must admit to chuckling a bit, though.

Bought this for my son who doesn't get to see this show anymore and he was very happy with it. I, as a mom, was happy with the fast shipping, easy ordering process, great condition of the merchandise and fair price.
An awesome gift and he loves it! Its totally like we are watching it on tv again! I love this series
My daughter loves this show, and asked for this as a gift. She watches them a lot, and is very happy with them.

this is my favorite show of all time when growing up in the 90's as a kid. very funny show sad that it ending. must buy. how many remembered when they all the episodes from start to finsih when the creator died.

I ordered the complete 1st and 2nd Seasons of Ed, Edd n Eddy.  I am soldily in my thirty's and these videos make me laugh like a child.  My 8 year old son loves them.  They are simple cartoons, but bring immense joy, to kids, and those who are kids at heart.
This is hands down one of the funniest cartoons I've seen in a long time, I love this show and all the characters. Can't get enough of it! Must buy you won't be disappointed.

I bought mine new. They came with a listing of shows for each season. Highlights of the series are any episodes which feature the Kanker Sisters, especially "Avast Ye Eds" and "Honor Thy Ed".
Special features on disc 1 - How to Make an Ed, Edd n Eddy Cartoon; Interview with the Creator; How to Draw Eddy; Cartoon Network Promos "28 Days Later" and "Crybaby", featuring Jimmy. All the features on disc 1 are fun.
Special features on disc 2 - "Behind the Eds" with the show's creator; How to draw Ed; Music video: "I'm Not Coming In Today"; Cartoon Network Promos "Ed's Origami" and "The Good the Bad and the Ugly". These are fun, also.
The features are a nice addition. They are fun. The show's creator, Danny Antonucci, is a blast.

Its awesome to see this title being released on dvd, i loved this show when it aired 10 years ago, and 22 years old still in love with the show, would like to see the rest of the seasons get released :] come one cartoon network!!
when i got the dvds right away i saw all the episodes and relived the cartoon i loved when i was a child i cant wait to see them all over again and show my future children the show
Ed, Edd 'n' Eddy has always been a favorite of my family, and these DVDs contained everything we wanted of the first and second seasons.
Awesome fun movie night for family fun.
Cheaper than buying individual seasons its funny I love
Loved
my grandson has watch these movies over and over again.  I might order more if there are any addtional ones to order.

These are the current prices listed on this site.

Price of Season 1 by itself: $6.99
Price of Season 2 by itself: $17.98
Price of this set (Seasons 1 and 2 together): $35.93

In other words, this set is charging people more than $10 extra and giving them no extra content to make up for it. If you want to buy this series on DVD, save yourself some money and buy Seasons 1 and 2 individually.
This show is really good. One of my favorite shows growing up, and still is one of the best cartoons I have ever seen. I highly recommend it!

The early seasons were great. Kids just trying to find something to do during a LONG summer vacation and also trying to make some change to buy jawbreakers of humongous size. Hilarious and done in an unusual wobbly style.
LOVED THIS SHOW AS A KID! Still love it as an adult. Now I can watch it all day long.
I wanted to watch this but I did not know where to watch so I thoguht about getting this for christmas or for any other occasion so I just got these just in time for christmas.
